      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "08:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "也算和你所知的斗兽场时代有联系吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "08:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "都是“黑暗时代”这段 就是西罗马灭亡后 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "08:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "说罗马输水渠的设计里有反沉积的斜坡和过滤装置  这在当时非常超前了 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "08:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "现在有些偏远地区的小型供水系统 原理也依照如此",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "08:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "这套系统一直沿用到罗马的中世纪 但是很荒谬的是...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "08:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "古时代人能搞懂的技术 中世纪的人却不明白 搞",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "08:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "只能眼睁睁看着水渠堵死 甚至拆石头去盖城堡 ",
