      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "没了  我了解的也不是很全面",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "话说你怎么想？祛魅的这个心理过程",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "感觉被背叛了？大概可以这样说吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "是因为你们文青把王家卫的电影奉为圣经",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "看着他那些瑰丽美妙的画面 就会下意识的认为他也是一个很美好文艺的人？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "我没有办法去接受拍出重庆森林的人私底下是一个那么猥琐俗气的人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "关于这点我似乎早就祛魅了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "在我们科研行业不端的行为屡见不鲜",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "突然想到了杨振宁",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "杨振宁还是伟大的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "无论如何他娶老婆的时候我没有跟风骂过他",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "喜欢青春的肉体我只能说是人之常情",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "我倾向于理解成 他在物理学上耗费了极大的心神和精力 所以就无法去很好的克制他的基础欲望",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "说来说去还是你们男的会给男的开脱  又是同行来着",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "在你的视角里觉得我们是男的抱团了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "我不这么觉得",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "杨振宁教授是女性 为科学领域做出巨大贡献后 也去找一个年纪差这么大的老公",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也不会认为有什么问题",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "你真的这么想吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "是啊 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "私德是私德  贡献是贡献 两者不能混为一谈",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "我不会去要求一个科学家拥有高尚的品德 尤其是在具有相当地位后仍旧保持艰苦朴素的精神",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你的意思是科学家就可以违法乱纪咯？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "享有特权",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "那我当然也不是这个意思",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是不是上头了？已经开始杠了 找角度",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "我没生气",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "认真和你说的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "好，你说你没生气 我就当你没生气",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也认真的和你说说我的看法",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得这个事情很简单 得看本身是不是自愿的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "首先排除了杨振宁和他的妻子是存在着权利不对等的关系",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "又不是非成年人  又不是学生和老师 上级和下属之间的关系",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "他们是作为两个成年人做下了决定",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以我觉得私德问题没什么好说的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "在我们中国从古到今的语境总是在追求完人  事实上是没有完人的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "他只是科学家 又不是圣人 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "再说了  私德很差人品极烂的哲学家也不在少数",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "康德：你在点我？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh说的就是你啊康德",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "就像我那天所说的  有些主观问题是没有争论的价值的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得讨厌杨振宁教授娶年轻貌美的老婆就和爱吃什么口味的豆花一样",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "都是私人的主观好恶",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "杨振宁教授的私生活 并不能抹杀他的贡献",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "其实说那么多  你无非就是想说道德和成就无关呗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "21:22",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "但我还是讨厌老夫少妻",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "21:22",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你可以讨厌啊 我也也没说我支持老夫少妻啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "21:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "喜欢甜豆花还是咸豆花都是个人的取向",
